data.description: Located in much sought after R-7 School Dist. This home sits on 2.48 acres of peace and quite. 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths is just the start of this charming home. The current owners raised a lovely family and hopes another great family ends up here to make their own memories! They have receipts for all the up keep and maintenance they have done on this home. Lots of space for a large family or just starting out. The finished walk out basement has a large family room with a wood burning fireplace and area for a play room or office and 4th bedroom. There is a 23x16 sun room with ceiling fan to enjoy all the beautiful season changes. Now for the kicker this home has a 20x30 detached garage with a 10x30 Lean To for that horse you have always wanted. Close to the Holcim Plant. Don't miss out on this one! Seller will consider any reasonable offer. Brokered And Advertised By: Realty Executives Five Star Listing Agent: Marilyn Green
